/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Dots</span><hr size=1> It is costing me a fortune to lvl cause of dots.  How do you all pay for them?  Do you cast on all group members?  Do you require payment up front?  How do you handle those that get ugly?   I am down to 37 dots and 17plat.  At this point if I dont require plat up front I just cant afford to cast temperance.  <br>
